  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/ed3c4aa2b9ecf438cc0cf8ca066c8a19.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world has fallen to the zombies, one munch at a time. Reduced to a mere handful of hardened survivors, the war is not over until the last human soldier stops breathing and starts shambling. Cursed Dawn is a blend of first person shooters and wave survival games, where every second brings you closer to death at the hands of the zombie hordes. Your job is to kill as many of them as possible before that happens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do that, you'll have to master the maps, packed to the rooftops with secrets to buy you a few seconds of life, stay on the move to avoid the horde overwhelming you, and most of all: Stay on your toes. No playthrough is the same, thanks to a dynamic spawn system that will hit you hard the moment you drop your guard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How long can you last?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/f1b52e8221910e81177093864a89ecb1.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=85 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arsenal of Weapons and Physics: You can fight zombies with over two dozen weapons. But why settle for just that? Blow them up, set them on fire, use explosives to fling them right into the incoming horde, turning bowling into a blood sport - or fling yourself across the map to get out of a tight spot!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/121865c88afffd8bc0dd80c5df4c657b.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/121865c88afffd8bc0dd80c5df4c657b.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>On Your Own or With Friends</strong>: Face the zombie hordes on your own, or bring a friend to explode zombies into heaps of gore, tag teaming monsters until death do you part</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/cda92de2896b894d5f7d389ee8746847.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/cda92de2896b894d5f7d389ee8746847.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/cda92de2896b894d5f7d389ee8746847.mp4?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open-Ended Strategic Gameplay</strong>: Fast fingers are good, but what will save you in the long run is fast thinking. Learn the map, the zombie types, and think fast on your feet (unless you want to become a B-ration for the zombies).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/922d79645f52a5316bc0e1e907c28e1b.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/922d79645f52a5316bc0e1e907c28e1b.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/922d79645f52a5316bc0e1e907c28e1b.mp4?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets Hidden Everywhere</strong>: Every map has codes to input, sequences to complete, aerial feats to complete, and seemingly inaccessible spots where you can find just the gun you need - unless the RNG decides you shall suffer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/7045e637c95be77548edf03f0e25b612.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/7045e637c95be77548edf03f0e25b612.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Gory World</strong>: Fight for your life across detailed maps, set in the darkest places of the world. Slaughterhouses. Catacombs. Mob hideouts. Carnivals. Elementary schools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/981b072b66a975c60348c06fa6a70443.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/981b072b66a975c60348c06fa6a70443.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More to Come</strong>: Cursed Dawn will expand with additional content after release, including new weapons, new enemy types, new maps and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.mp4?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
