_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/922d79645f52a5316bc0e1e907c28e1b.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/922d79645f52a5316bc0e1e907c28e1b.mp4?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secrets Hidden Everywhere</strong>: Every map has codes to input, sequences to complete, aerial feats to complete, and seemingly inaccessible spots where you can find just the gun you need - unless the RNG decides you shall suffer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/7045e637c95be77548edf03f0e25b612.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/7045e637c95be77548edf03f0e25b612.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Gory World</strong>: Fight for your life across detailed maps, set in the darkest places of the world. Slaughterhouses. Catacombs. Mob hideouts. Carnivals. Elementary schools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/981b072b66a975c60348c06fa6a70443.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/981b072b66a975c60348c06fa6a70443.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More to Come</strong>: Cursed Dawn will expand with additional content after release, including new weapons, new enemy types, new maps and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.poster.avif?t=1771620177\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.webm?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713550/extras/d8186cec3dcc6950cf13a4a5320767ed.mp4?t=1771620177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
